JURISDICTIONAL MOTIONS OVERRULED

92-1354. Bank One, Columbus, N.A. v. O’Brien.

Franklin County, Nos. 91AP-166 and 91AP-441. On motion to certify the record and on motion for leave to file memorandum in support instanter. Motions denied.

Wright, J., dissents. H. Brown, J., not participating.
